{"tid":356521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究 多數男人生殖器　已經變成香菇的形狀","createTime":"2017-08-12T06:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T11:48:41.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97d3cc3a0c1c29b59b3b0a00da362a380144dc5a","tid":356521,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"報告針對1千名男性進行統計，結果發現，有高達40%讀者稱自己的陰莖形狀，宛如「香菇」的頭大身體小。此外有25%讀者指出生殖器變成「向上彎曲」如香蕉的形狀，有22%稱是「頭小身體大」如紅蘿蔔的形狀。最後有13%讀者表示生殖器已經變成「彎彎」的形狀，有些讀者表示生殖器出現不規則扭曲，而這很有可能是罹患佩羅尼氏病(Peyronie's Disease，又稱曲甲症)的前兆，這很有可能引發勃起障礙。台灣網友則表示：「台男已經進化到金針菇型態了XD」、「現在是香菇形狀？以前是什麼形狀？蛇頭嗎？」、「金針菇、柳松菇、鴻禧菇...請選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170812/640_8c87ba0acf6fde0c126453c770eebb5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170812%2F640_8c87ba0acf6fde0c126453c770eebb5d.jpg&h=2e5eb258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096377191b78e977539c72e9410284da6923e493","tid":356521,"uid":94115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"Bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f914713358e299f02810789499deff966eeedab","tid":356521,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔好以為cosplay左就唔叫露 bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c353685c5b1f7c9c865bedf778f81193cf06289","tid":356521,"uid":68528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f524d9aedc5068a160afb3c715d98f40a8d97b68","tid":356521,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"唔好以為生得似香菇就唔使bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/